Changes the port number associated with this socket address.

# Examples

```
use std::net::{SocketAddrV4, Ipv4Addr};

let mut socket = SocketAddrV4::new(Ipv4Addr::new(127, 0, 0, 1), 8080);
socket.set_port(4242);
assert_eq!(socket.port(), 4242);
```
